items.name: Stakan
items.description: "стакан" (stakan) is a Russian term that translates to "order book" in English.  What is an Order Book? An order book is a real-time list of buy and sell orders on a trading platform. It shows:  Bid orders (buy orders) – Traders wanting to buy an asset at a specific price. Ask orders (sell orders) – Traders willing to sell at a certain price.

items.name: TheEndingofOldLife
items.description: It was a cold autumn afternoon, the sunlight barely piercing through the thick canopy above. She stopped by an ancient oak tree, its bark scarred by time, and took a deep breath. That’s when she heard it—the softest echo of her name.  “Lena…” it called again, barely a whisper, but it was clear. The voice wasn’t hers. Her heart skipped a beat.
